A MOTHER who knifed her little son to <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" target="_blank">death</a> and cut out his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heart" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heart" target="_blank">heart</a> believed she was on a mission from God a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court" target="_blank">court</a> heard todayA <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judge" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judge" target="_blank">judge</a> ruled that Farai Chirashi 32 was <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Insanity" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Insanity" target="_blank">insane</a> when she <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder" target="_blank">killed</a> her fiveyearold boy ScottHe <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acquittal" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acquittal" target="_blank">acquitted</a> her of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder_in_English_law" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder_in_English_law" target="_blank">murder</a> and ordered her to be detained in a secure <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Psychiatric_hospital" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Psychiatric_hospital" target="_blank">mental hospital</a> without limit of timeA <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Senior_status" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Senior_status" target="_blank">senior</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Psychiatrist" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Psychiatrist" target="_blank">psychiatrist</a> told the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court" target="_blank">High Court</a> in <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow" target="_blank">Glasgow</a> that Chirashi had a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Psychosis" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Psychosis" target="_blan